# translation_lang = en
# prose_translation = It is necessary, therefore, that a well-constructed plot be simple rather than double, as some say, and that the change be not to good fortune from misfortune, but on the contrary from good fortune to misfortune, and not because of wickedness but because of a great error, or one like that which has been mentioned, or better rather than worse.
